item.title: Issue 1 March 1st to March 7th,2020
item.description: The Olb City Announcer Volume 1, Issue 1 March 1st- March 7th, 2020 Gold Mine Found! by Tony Yuan and Clint Lee West AM District-On Tuesday, an ancient gold mine was found in the district of West AM, known to locals as West-A-Mountain district. The gold mine was discovered by Jack Peterson, a native resident, when he was volunteering to pick up trash.
